        "eyebrow": "THE INVITATION",
        "heading": "Beyond the Mantle: Your Sovereign Sanctuary",
        "paragraph_1": "The House of Vuu was born from a story of survival turned into triumph—a reality you can now see, touch, and wear. But we believe that true sovereignty is not just worn; it is inhabited.",
